tournament.motion:
THR the popularity of true crime entertainment

True crime is a nonfiction literary, podcast, and film genre in which the author examines an actual crime and details the actions of real people associated with and affected by criminal events. True crime media explores a variety of crimes including heinous crimes such as murder, serial killings, torture and cannibalism. Some true crime media also choose to focus on unsolved crimes or alleged crimes

TH prefers a world where people do not feel the emotion of pride

Pride refers to the emotion of having a high opinion of oneself or one's own importance, qualities and actions

TH, as the feminist movement, would promote the ‘snail girl era’ narrative

In contrast to narratives such as the ‘girlboss narrative’, the 'snail girl era' encourages young women to live a slower, more relaxed lifestyle. This narrative emphasises the importance of prioritising a slower life of happiness,self-care, and non material fulfilment over hustle culture and traditional success
THW allow people raised in isolated communities (e.g. the Amish, Hasidic Jews) to sue their communities for harms caused by their lifestyle

TH R the rise of self-diagnosis

Self-diagnosis is the process of individuals diagnosing or identifying medical conditions themselves based on information online
TH R the rise of fitness influencers

TH, as the Democratic Party of the United States, prefers a world where the assassination of Donald Trump had been successful

On July 13, 2024, Donald Trump, a former president of the United States and the Republican Party's presumptive nominee in the 2024 presidential election, survived an assassination attempt while addressing a campaign rally near Butler, Pennsylvania. Trump was shot and wounded in his right ear but sustained no fatal or major injuries
